<br>
It gives you access to spells and effects you dont otherwise get, but generally the cost is too expensive to make selling them to other players near impossible except for certain things like SoW potions....<br>
<br>
That said I have spent the 15k or so to keep my skill maxed for level through 53......  Its a labor of love. <p>Lorec <br>
